miraculous, isn&apos;t the only miraculous </div><div class="t me x29 h27 y18d ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">story in the Bible. Look up these texts and the stories surrounding </div><div class="t ma9 x29 h27 yd6 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them. What miracles do they depict? </div><div class="t m19b x47 h27 y18e ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gen. 21:2 </div><div class="t m3f x60 h27 y18e ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m172 x69 h27 y18e ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m19c x49 h27 y18f ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Exod. 13:21, 22 </div><div class="t m3f xb h27 y18f ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m172 x69 h27 y18f ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m19d x47 h27 y190 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dan. 5:5, 24-29 </div><div class="t m3f x6a h27 y190 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m172 x69 h27 y190 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t mce x47 h27 y191 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 1:20 </div><div class="t m3f x51 h27 y192 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m172 x69 h27 y192 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m19e x47 h27 y193 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mark 6:44 </div><div class="t m3f x51 h27 y193 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m172 x69 h27 y193 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m4b x20 h27 y194 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How can these accounts be explained other than by the super-</div><div class="t m19f x1d h27 y195 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">natural intervention of God? Thus, how foolhardy to dismiss </div><div class="t m1a0 x1d h27 y196 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">any part of the Bible because of supernatural acts that go be-</div><div class="t m1a1 x1d h27 y197 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">yond what our basic logic, reason, and science tell us. If any-</div><div class="t m1a2 x1d h27 y198 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thing, these stories should show us just how limited our science, </div><div class="t m1a3 x1d h27 y199 ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our logic, and our reason can be when it comes to the things of </div><div class="t m198 x6f h27 y19a ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. </div><div class="t m1a4 x46 h16 y19b ff2 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
